OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager killed in south-west London
OL,6,FA 14-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after a teenager was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death in south-west London.
OL,10,FJamal Coombes, 17, died after a
OL,11,Fconfrontation in Glycena Road,
OL,12,FBattersea, at 4.20am on Saturday.
OL,14,FPolice had appealed for witnesses who
OL,15,Fsaw a group of men running away to
OL,16,Fcome forward.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
