OL,3,CBoy, 14, charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager killed in south-west London
OL,6,FThe 14-year-old boy, who has not been
OL,7,Fnamed because of his age, will appear
OL,8,Fat Highbury Corner Youth Court on
OL,9,FMonday accused of murder and
OL,10,Fpossession of a knife.
OL,12,FA boy and a girl, both aged 15, who
OL,13,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,14,Fon Saturday have been released on
OL,15,Fbail, while another boy, also aged 15,
OL,16,Fwas arrested on suspicion of murder on
OL,17,FSunday and remains in custody.
